
"What are you sorry for ?" My eyes were about to pop out, "We were both drunk and we lost control and we ... Leena, I'm really sorry" His eyes were filled with regret, I didn't know what to say or do, I was completely shocked, I never thought things would go this far.
"Now you're sorry?" I started crying,
"Don't blame it on me ! You wanted to drink and YOU convinced me to take you to the club!"
"Now you're just being a jerk"
"Listen to me, Leena ... it's not working"
"What do you mean ?" I shot my head up and glared at him.
"Us, it's not working between us. We should break up"
"WHAT ? NOW YOU'RE BREAKING UP WITH ME ? AFTER WHAT HAPPENED BETWEEN US"
"It's normal, this thing happens a lot, it's not a rare thing at all"
"YOU DONT UNDERSTAND ! ITS ONE OF THE HUGEST SINS ANYBODY CAN DO ! ITS NOT A NORMAL THING! And now, you're just throwing me away after you got what you were after"
"No, No ! That's not what I was after ! I was after you ! The old you ! I loved the girl with loose modest clothes, the girl that looks at the ground not at boys, the girl that shows nothing more than her palms and face ! I didn't love the girl with shorts and visible chest!" He opened the door and walked out the room.
"No! Please ! Stay! You can't just leave ! You need to marry me !" I cried after him.
"No Leena, YOU need me to marry you. You know what, I'd be lying if I say that I didn't like the new Leena, I'd be lying. I enjoyed your lips, I was happy while staring at your curves, but I wasn't in love, I loved your look and body, and stopped loving your soul, and this doesn't work. All girls have the same body, but it's the soul and emotions that matter" He was getting into his shoese.
"BUT I GAVE YOU EVERYTHING".
"And that was the problem, I fell for the girl that was protective and modest, not the one that gives it all. Any girl can give me everything for some dollars" He said and walked out the house.
I lied on the couch, crying, screaming and then started throwing things around, I broke 2 vases, a table, the radio and some other things.